data.value: -Please ensure to enable Usb Debugging on your phone . -Add platform-tools folder to path in system environment variable One time. tutorial https://youtu.be/WbRlwNPKOSY -Location of platform-tools example: C:\Program Files (x86)\Unity\Hub\Editor\2020.3.10f1\Editor\Data\PlaybackEngines\AndroidPlayer\SDK\platform-tools -Connect USB to your phone. -Press Connect. -Remove your usb. -Open unity remote. -Open unity-> Project Setting-> editor -> Any Android Device.
